did.abstract: The University of Kentucky Libraries Special Collections Research Center. University Archives Athletics General Reference Files (dated 1880-2009; 25.99 cubic feet; 51 document boxes, 2 record storage cartons, 1 flat box) primarily comprise newspaper clippings and press releases that document varsity and intramural athletics at the University of Kentucky, including games, rivalries, and tournaments; coaches, players, and mascots; clubs; and issues, including civil rights.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The University of Kentucky Libraries Special Collections Research Center. University Archives Athletics General Reference Files (dated 1880-2009; 25.99 cubic feet; 51 document boxes, 2 record storage cartons, 1 flat box) primarily comprise newspaper clippings and press releases that document varsity and intramural athletics at the University of Kentucky, including games, rivalries, and tournaments; coaches, players, and mascots; clubs; and issues, including civil rights. Sports represented include football, men's basketball, and women's basketball (Lady Kats).

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: The physical rights to the materials in this collection are held by the University of Kentucky Special Collections Research Center.
